頭髮幾短？"},{"pid":"9f81522aac11010ce683f3d615af7e8f6ea9fded","tid":345420,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"我之前都係咁好濃密，之後開始少頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bad504b4be869b87aa6ce64abb19c150b6d4db4","tid":345420,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"有無諗過電直佢， 或者電曲"},{"pid":"bed9570a9e53664b8cc7820ef06d77b199f4ebf5","tid":345420,"uid":16480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T20:07:55.000Z","msg":"硬同微曲先正喎<br />\n完全唔驚個頭會塔<br />\n剪短少少 一起身用風筒吹一吹就出得門口 頭都唔使gel"},{"pid":"9b4deb8b47b1dd36ec6e5ea9df6319d053741d40","tid":345420,"uid":7458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T05:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我就係咁<br />\n仲要係絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔都話唔太覺<br />\n夏天濕度高出街唔洗比風吹都會自己亂哂<br />\n好羨慕人地d頭髮又幼又順<br />\n成世人都係短頭髮<br />\n長無我份</blockquote><br />\n絲打 頭髮幾短？</blockquote><br />\n長到去下巴左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時後面d頭髮會翹起"},{"pid":"909f723b757a3d7c14c89da831ad04f5f4d93539","tid":345420,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬同微曲先正喎<br />\n完全唔驚個頭會塔<br />\n剪短少少 一起身用風筒吹一吹就出得門口 頭都唔使gel</blockquote><br />\n肯撚定唔會係你自己想要果隻<br />\n曲到不規則、一大餅野<br />\n左右上都一大舊頂出來<br />\n<br />\n3~4星期剪一次頭少不免<br />\n煩到嘔電<br />\n型唔會有份<br />\n教gel 頭方法都用唔到在自己身上<br />\n<br />\n你d 幻想同想要個家姐<br />\n會整野你食照顧你好溫柔介紹女仔你識一撚樣<br />\n咁不切實際<br />\n大俠事必要有型靚仔只係你呢d 升斗市民一廂情願的想法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鳩毛頭只係好過地中海"},{"pid":"ecf4b0450b7df4017a66be35cc5d58b167d7bf78","tid":345420,"uid":30222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"日日朝早用20-30分鐘洗頭吹直gel 頭先出得門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好痛苦"},{"pid":"aae426dd3850b63c5b015dcbf3a91d9993c10ff4","tid":345420,"uid":54490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41f02b29cdacdb3f0594725ce10261a67a5347f4","tid":345420,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"直髮先靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34bb0846cf655e1b482ff56813eb7f258e1f438","tid":345420,"uid":63974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"唔電直基本無解"},{"pid":"488ab6f90e8ab70386b3360bcc0bc7e1cf0dbce1","tid":345420,"uid":128309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:10:42.000Z","msg":"硬到好似陰毛生上頭 個零月唔剪就好似戴左頭盔咁 次次剪頭髮都一定要產兩邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係身邊啲朋友話好羨慕曲髮 其實你地明唔明天生曲同電出黎個種曲係唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107ed9470e7d993d036495eb7a77a4e68219cc9a","tid":345420,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"一樣係生到好似鳩毛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲陰攣到向上捲，想佢捲返落黎又要濕頭先做到<br />\n<br />\n個面型唔留陰又唔好睇<br />\n<br />\n頭髮一長真係好似戴左頭盔咁<br />\n<br />\n剪髮鏟兩邊又係唔岩個面型<br />\n<br />\n問個髮型師，電髮好唔好，佢仲話我以為夠攣洗乜電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無髮型可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f67960f43d6d749c254da0eff779d99a727c5583","tid":345420,"uid":62964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:29:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/26cd0001cdbcd4dff039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F26cd0001cdbcd4dff039&h=764fc421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冬天都叫做好啲 攣到咁既樣<br />\n但一到夏天個頭就是好似爆炸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0217240a84aa2a1ef037007b2fb4f3bf5760d382","tid":345420,"uid":54910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:31:21.000Z","msg":"唔撚可以留長 長期兩邊後面鏟青 上面都勁位同冇陰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfdeadf899d13608a522e27b82dd2d6ca2e6d51","tid":345420,"uid":54910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔撚可以留長 長期兩邊後面鏟青 上面都勁位同冇陰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n短"},{"pid":"1b736c08cb17ff49d1d4c495723d28f576fc97c9","tid":345420,"uid":122632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T07:45:04.000Z","msg":"屌完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都要洗頭真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"061b9f47114d494ce8c7d90b9066426e804e9b94","tid":345420,"uid":58076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T08:37:49.000Z","msg":"最憎係冇乜fd一樣生到9毛咁，個個都話想攣，其實咁ge髮質好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一長就戴頭盔咁，又厚，又難長<br />\n長到某個位好似停止生長咁，然後慢慢變厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa68249b3fff69dad742b863db4c646ecb67127","tid":345420,"uid":63974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日都要洗頭真係好撚煩</blockquote><br />\n係啊 仲有曲髮已經好易乾 日日洗兩次真係乾到仆街"}]}